title: Rangers win AL West on final day, Hamels beat Angels 9-2
text:
> Top News Rangers win AL West on final day, Hamels beat Angels 9-2 Texas Rangers' Hanser Alberto runs onto the field after the final out of the baseball game against the Los Angeles Angels in Arlington, Texas, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015. The Rangers clinched the AL West title on the last day of the regular season with the 9-2 win. (AP Photo/LM Otero)
